HEADWORD: Inculpatory
<hw>In*cul"pa*to*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Imputing
blame; causing blame to be imputed to; criminatory; compromising;
implicating. Opposite of <ant>exculpatory</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

